#. +> trunk6 stable6
#: ui/OutputPanel.qml:201
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"Determines how much padding is put around the image sent to the display to "
"compensate for part of the content being cut off around the edges.<nl/><nl/"
">This is sometimes needed when using a TV as a screen."
msgstr ""
"画面の端が切れてしまうのを防ぐために、出力映像に挿入する余白を設定します。"
"<nl/><nl/>テレビを画面として利用する際に必要になることがあります。"

#. +> trunk6 stable6
#: ui/OutputPanel.qml:206
#, kde-format
msgid "RGB range:"
msgstr "RGB レンジ:"

#. +> stable5
#: package/contents/ui/OutputPanel.qml:189
#, kde-format
msgid "RGB Range:"
msgstr "RGB レンジ:"

#. +> trunk6 stable6 stable5
#: ui/OutputPanel.qml:215
#, kde-format
msgid "Full"
msgstr "フル"

#. +> trunk6 stable6 stable5
#: ui/OutputPanel.qml:216
#, kde-format
msgid "Limited"
msgstr "リミテッド"

#. +> trunk6 stable6
#: ui/OutputPanel.qml:226
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"Determines whether the range of possible color values needs to be limited "
"for the display. This should only be changed if the colors on the screen "
"look washed out."
msgstr ""
"ディスプレイの色の範囲を制限するかどうかを設定します。画面の色が白っぽく見え"
"る場合にのみこの設定を変更してください。"

#. +> stable5
#: package/contents/ui/OutputPanel.qml:73
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"&quot;%1&quot; is the only resolution supported by this display.<nl/><nl/"
">Using unsupported resolutions was possible in the Plasma X11 session, but "
"they were never guaranteed to work and are not available in this Plasma "
"Wayland session."
msgstr ""
"&quot;%1&quot; は、このディスプレイによってサポートされている唯一の解像度で"
"す。<nl/><nl/>サポートされていない解像度の使用は Plasma X11 セッションでは可"
"能でしたが、Plasma Wayland セッションでは不可能です。"

#. +> trunk6 stable6
#: ui/OutputPanel.qml:233
#, kde-format
